{
  "id": "6a106488a10e2dac24d2e16d",
  "title": "みんなこれ下手だなと思っていること",
  "created": 1779459213,
  "updated": 1779463329,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "6a106488a10e2dac24d2e16d",
      "text": "みんなこれ下手だなと思っていること",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1779459213,
      "updated": 1779459213
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1064a30000000000847c82",
      "text": "from [2026/05/18]",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1779459235,
      "updated": 1779459989
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1067350000000000fbcf7a",
      "text": "> 最近、自分が得意だと思っていることはどちらかというと[好きなこと]に近く、みんなこれ[下手]だなと思っていることが[得意なこと]に近いんだと気付いた",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1779459893,
      "updated": 1779459964
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1067390000000000fbcf7b",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1779459897,
      "updated": 1779459897
    },
    {
      "id": "6a10648d0000000000847c80",
      "text": " Cosenseの使い方[yosider.icon]",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1779459213,
      "updated": 1779459380
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1065340000000000847c83",
      "text": "  と井戸端で書いたら誤解を生みそうだ",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1779459380,
      "updated": 1779459531
    },
    {
      "id": "6a10648f0000000000847c81",
      "text": " [誤字脱字]の発見[yosider.icon]",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1779459215,
      "updated": 1779462977
    },
    {
      "id": "6a10690d0000000000aa1c1d",
      "text": "  その代わり自分は思考のスピードが遅そう",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1779460364,
      "updated": 1779460398
    },
    {
      "id": "6a10720e0000000000621568",
      "text": "   その組み合わせだと、思考のスピードが目先の誤り発見に阻害されていそう[Summer498.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1779462670,
      "updated": 1779462711
    },
    {
      "id": "6a10729e00000000004da699",
      "text": "   なんか、誤字が多い人は書いた文を振り返らずに[がーっと書き続け]ているイメージがある[yosider.icon]",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1779462813,
      "updated": 1779463008
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1072d300000000004da69a",
      "text": "   それに対して自分は1行毎に見直している気がする",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1779462865,
      "updated": 1779462901
    },
    {
      "id": "6a10730100000000004da69b",
      "text": "    誤字を発見するためというわけではなく、書いたことが自分の考えを正確に表現しているか確かめたい",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1779462911,
      "updated": 1779462967
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1072b10000000000621569",
      "text": "\t\t\t丁寧に読むのが得意そう[Summer498.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1779462834,
      "updated": 1779462972
    },
    {
      "id": "6a10733c000000000062156c",
      "text": "\t\t\t\t得意というか癖になってそう",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1779462973,
      "updated": 1779462982
    },
    {
      "id": "6a107346000000000062156d",
      "text": "\t\t\t\t自分の文章だけではなく誰の文章も丁寧に読んで誤字もついでに見つけ出してそう",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1779462983,
      "updated": 1779463022
    },
    {
      "id": "6a10739900000000004da69c",
      "text": "\t\t\t\t どうだろう そうなのかな[yosider.icon]",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1779463063,
      "updated": 1779463117
    },
    {
      "id": "6a10742a00000000004da69d",
      "text": "\t\t\t\t [本を読む時、頭の中で音読]しがちなのが関係あるかも",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1779463209,
      "updated": 1779463245
    },
    {
      "id": "6a10746a00000000004da69e",
      "text": "\t\t\t\t  読む速度にリミットがかかり誤字に気づきやすくなる",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1779463273,
      "updated": 1779463300
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1072de000000000062156a",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1779462879,
      "updated": 1779462879
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1072de000000000062156b",
      "text": "[Summer498.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1779462879,
      "updated": 1779463107
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1073c4000000000062156f",
      "text": "\t古典論理的思考",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1779463109,
      "updated": 1779463329
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1073c2000000000062156e",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1779463107,
      "updated": 1779463107
    }
  ]
}